reviewer: maintainer-review
risk: high
confidence: medium
sprint: governance-followups
release: vnext
reporter: codex-agent
severity: medium
environment: linux
repro_steps: Run large governance normalization over cross-owned items and observe repetitive ownership conflict handling.
affected_version: 2026.3.12
component: governance-batch-ownership
regression: false
customer_impact: Maintainers can execute approved governance maintenance faster with explicit safety evidence.
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-04T21:55:27.146Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm search 'ownership conflict force audit override workflow' --limit 20; pm search 'ownership-safe batch mutation mode governance override' --limit 20; pm list-open --limit 20. Net-new because current items improve guidance only; no feature currently provides plan+execute batch ownership override workflow for governance operations."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-04T21:55:27.146Z",codex-agent,Design should separate planning and execution phases and require explicit operator confirmation before any forced mutation batch.
